Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a storybook vision of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you leave me behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Heaven, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin' bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You followed me here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Namatame Taro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the ones I saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This dude high or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to save this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Nanako back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You put the people you saw on the Midnight Channel into this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On rainy nights... on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they signal me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't put you in the TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how would you have ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that we wouldn't have been able to face ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we nearly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's completely lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you! "Save," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just killing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you plan on killing this child.
