Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}still hasn't recovered from her cold.{... FUCKING JAPAN}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}And then to go through that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Nana's still so small,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:16.08,Default,,0090,0090,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}so her other self didn't appear like it did for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}And she got caught in all that craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}All those Shadows just had to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}There's no way she could've handled that, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}Why did I waste time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}listening to what Namatame had to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}If I hadn't tried to engage him in conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,717)}and we'd rescued Nanako immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, it isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i}is{\i0} my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, I prioritized solving the case over Nanako's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, Nanako is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enough of this pity party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is feeling pathetic and consoling each other gonna solve anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you desperately trying to save Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys. Acting all gloomy won't solve anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think how Nanako would feel if she saw us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, you were pretty cool for once, Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, don't make a scene in the hospital. Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the fog especially thick today?{so's my dick}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and it's really cold, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check this out. It's about Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he regained consciousness this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"According to the police interrogation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he confessed that he regrets what he did and admits that he was just scared."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he admitted to his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At long last.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received word from the hospital this morning that it's okay to visit Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should go see her when school lets out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Nanako's doing a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God.{CHRISTIAN PROPAGANDA}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to invite her too, but she wasn't in her classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Nanako's doing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just having a hard time believing that the case is truly over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're a unique person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You referred to me as your friend, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what you said at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm glad you were there."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted someone to acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was trying so desperately to solve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take away my ability as a detective, I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you were happy that I was there. {typo in stream}{thank you for leaving it in}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me a place where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're headed for the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, weren't we going to see Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still just lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, y-you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
