Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1235,690)}urse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you're not! Are you {\i1}trying{\i0} to send Nanako back to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is {dog}Narukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:21:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a sudden change in Nanako's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry over to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a family member?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your big brother's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.39,0:22:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even looked at some space heaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go buy one together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make snowmen when it snows.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised that we'd play together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.50,0:24:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come he's the one who gets to live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.21,0:24:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must... reach out to the truth.
